WEBVTT

00:00:57.454 --> 00:01:00.954
sat on the drum set
we had assembled in the living room

00:01:02.454 --> 00:01:04.079
and started beating it.

00:01:05.413 --> 00:01:06.829
Ten seconds.

00:01:07.913 --> 00:01:09.413
Thirty seconds.

00:01:10.288 --> 00:01:11.913
Fifty seconds.

00:01:12.913 --> 00:01:14.246
A minute.

00:01:15.079 --> 00:01:17.246
A light came on in the hallway.

00:01:18.329 --> 00:01:20.204
One minute and 20 seconds.

00:01:21.288 --> 00:01:24.829
A man was standing at the door,
hesitant to press the bell.

00:01:26.038 --> 00:01:28.538
One minute and 52 seconds.

00:01:29.163 --> 00:01:30.996
The doorbell rang,